The paper discusses a new attack against face recognition systems using adversarial examples and infrared illumination. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and cybersecurity (cs.CR) sub-categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques (cs.MM) and could be relevant to researchers working on adversarial attacks (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
